                <note rend="inline" type="source">810.79611 Pan American Airways, Inc./675:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Summerlin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-10-09T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 9, 1929—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>76. Do you consider that the present time is favorable for Pan American Airways
                    to apply for an operating concession in Honduras?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
